Holders of the Congressional
Medal of Honor are eligible for
full medical and hospital care in
Veterans Administration hospi-
tails if the disability is due to
wartime or peacetime service.


Those Medal of Honor winners
who performed acts Of heroism
during wartime are also entitled
to a payment of $500 a month
if they are age so or older. A
bill to award the same payment
to those whose acts of heroism
we're performed during peace
time is now being considered by
the Congress.


There are 284 Medal of Honor
winners living.

Hames. Jr., of2750 E. Tamarisk,
he told police he loaned the car
to Miss Warren. He also claimed

81 ,634 In cash found on the dead
woman belonged to him.
